Sunflower to Invest 30 Million Shekels in Israeli Solar-Energy Projects

-- B y   G w e n   A c k e r m a n
-- 
2011-03-10T07:47:01Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/sunflower-to-invest-30-million-shekels-in-israeli-solar-energy-projects.html
  Sunflower Sustainable Investments
Ltd. (SNFL)  said it has agreed to invest 30 million shekels to build
dozens of photovoltaic solar-energy projects in  Israel .
Sunflower made the announcement in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
